    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014not a single blemish to be found anywhere. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
