      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, which has been meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. This specimen delivers linear power delivery to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement and an undiluted suspension geometry utilizing fresh bushings and OEM-plus dampers. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the interior leather remains supple and free of typical bolster wear. A mechanically flawless, collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast.",
